to self-doubt, doesn't mind losing a tempo to provoke the weakening ...h7-h6.}
h6 {Pretty much necessary,} ({since after} 13... Nf6 14. Bd2 {, White can
continue to mass up on the kingside.}) 14. Ngf3 Rfd8 {Clearing the f8-square
